OL,6,F"Some kind of justice. Some kind of
OL,7,Fanswers for the family. Some closure
OL,8,Ffor us all.
OL,10,F"As it stands Dylan's lost his life.
OL,11,FSomebody is responsible for it and
OL,12,Fthere has been no punishment at all."
OL,14,F"The worst thing he ever did was leave
OL,15,Fhim," she added. "As a parent how
OL,16,Fcould you leave my boy on the road
OL,17,Fdying and that is all I wanted him
OL,18,Fcharged with.
