OL,4,Cvictim's mum's plea
OL,6,F"You left him, it's bad enough you
OL,7,Fhurt him but to leave him dying in the
OL,8,Farms of his friend that's
OL,9,Funforgivable."
OL,11,FAn inquest into Dylan's death, which
OL,12,Fbegan in 2021, was halted when a
OL,13,Fcoroner referred the case back to the
OL,14,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS) asking
OL,15,Ffor a charge of gross negligence.
OL,17,FBut, this was denied.
