OL,3,C'I can't give up': Hit and run
OL,4,Cvictim's mum's plea
OL,6,FThe inquest finally concluded in
OL,7,FJanuary 2024 where the coroner Dr
OL,8,FJames Adeley ruled it was in the
OL,9,F"interests of justice" to name Mr
OL,10,FHarwood once more.
OL,12,FIt found Mr Harwood had likely drunk
OL,13,Fthree pints of lager and two glasses
OL,14,Fof wine before Dylan's death.
OL,16,FHe had been rushing to meet a woman he
OL,17,Fhad started talking to on a dating app
OL,18,Fand was putting her postcode into his
OL,19,Fsat nav when he hit Dylan, the inquest
OL,20,Fwas told.
