OL,3,C'I can't give up': Hit and run
OL,4,Cvictim's mum's plea
OL,6,FThe inquest also heard how Mr Harwood
OL,7,Fdid not know what he had hit, despite
OL,8,Fthe hole in the windscreen caused by
OL,9,FDylan's head and did not slow down or
OL,10,Fstop.
OL,12,FHe carried on to the address and
OL,13,Fhanded himself in to the police the
OL,14,Ffollowing day.
OL,16,FThe police watchdog is investigating
OL,17,Fthree officers who dealt with the
OL,18,Fcrash, but Ms Milligan believes the
OL,19,Fcommunity could have evidence to help
OL,20,Fexplain what really happened.
