OL,3,C'I can't give up': Hit and run
OL,4,Cvictim's mum's plea
OL,6,F"We need people to come forward," she
OL,7,Fsaid. "People know what happened that
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,F"It must be playing on people's minds
OL,11,Fthat they have got information they
OL,12,Fcould just help us with.
OL,14,F"And that's where my fight comes from
OL,15,Fbecause I know I can't give up. I
OL,16,Fcan't give up because he took the best
OL,17,Fthing out of my life."
